{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":603,"text":"So, this book that I have in my hand"},{"time":3669,"text":"is a directory of everybody who had an email address"},{"time":7603,"text":"in 1982. (Laughter)"},{"time":11122,"text":"Actually, it's deceptively large."},{"time":14807,"text":"There's actually only about 20 people on each page,"},{"time":18244,"text":"because we have the name, address"},{"time":20134,"text":"and telephone number of every single person."},{"time":23227,"text":"And, in fact, everybody's listed twice,"},{"time":25410,"text":"because it's sorted once by name and once by email address."},{"time":29968,"text":"Obviously a very small community."},{"time":32869,"text":"There were only two other Dannys on the Internet then."},{"time":36300,"text":"I knew them both."},{"time":37900,"text":"We didn't all know each other,"},{"time":39656,"text":"but we all kind of trusted each other,"},{"time":42769,"text":"and that basic feeling of trust"},{"time":46567,"text":"permeated the whole network,"},{"time":49154,"text":"and there was a real sense that"},{"time":51511,"text":"we could depend on each other to do things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54517,"text":"So just to give you an idea of the level of trust in this community,"},{"time":58092,"text":"let me tell you what it was like"},{"time":59717,"text":"to register a domain name in the early days."},{"time":63822,"text":"Now, it just so happened that I got to register"},{"time":66452,"text":"the third domain name on the Internet."},{"time":68912,"text":"So I could have anything I wanted"},{"time":70560,"text":"other than bbn.com and symbolics.com."},{"time":75005,"text":"So I picked think.com, but then I thought,"},{"time":78419,"text":"you know, there's a lot of really interesting names out there."},{"time":81405,"text":"Maybe I should register a few extras just in case."},{"time":85614,"text":"And then I thought, \"Nah, that wouldn't be very nice.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":88898,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":94593,"text":"That attitude of only taking what you need"},{"time":98222,"text":"was really what everybody had on the network in those days,"},{"time":102266,"text":"and in fact, it wasn't just the people on the network,"},{"time":105563,"text":"but it was actually kind of built into the protocols"},{"time":108283,"text":"of the Internet itself."},{"time":110227,"text":"So the basic idea of I.P., or Internet protocol,"},{"time":114086,"text":"and the way that the -- the routing algorithm that used it,"},{"time":117815,"text":"were fundamentally \"from each according to their ability,"},{"time":121944,"text":"to each according to their need.\""},{"time":124062,"text":"And so, if you had some extra bandwidth,"},{"time":127075,"text":"you'd deliver a message for someone."},{"time":128518,"text":"If they had some extra bandwidth, they would deliver a message for you."},{"time":131511,"text":"You'd kind of depend on people to do that,"},{"time":133525,"text":"and that was the building block."},{"time":136189,"text":"It was actually interesting that such a communist principle"},{"time":138816,"text":"was the basis of a system developed during the Cold War"},{"time":141252,"text":"by the Defense Department,"},{"time":143683,"text":"but it obviously worked really well,"},{"time":146753,"text":"and we all saw what happened with the Internet."},{"time":150196,"text":"It was incredibly successful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152468,"text":"In fact, it was so successful that there's no way"},{"time":155765,"text":"that these days you could make a book like this."},{"time":159353,"text":"My rough calculation is it would be about 25 miles thick."},{"time":165519,"text":"But, of course, you couldn't do it,"},{"time":166693,"text":"because we don't know the names of all the people"},{"time":168483,"text":"with Internet or email addresses,"},{"time":171557,"text":"and even if we did know their names,"},{"time":173089,"text":"I'm pretty sure that they would not want their name,"},{"time":175522,"text":"address and telephone number published to everyone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179818,"text":"So the fact is that there's a lot of bad guys on the Internet these days,"},{"time":183520,"text":"and so we dealt with that by making"},{"time":187691,"text":"walled communities,"},{"time":189590,"text":"secure subnetworks, VPNs,"},{"time":194327,"text":"little things that aren't really the Internet"},{"time":195923,"text":"but are made out of the same building blocks,"},{"time":197894,"text":"but we're still basically building it out of those"},{"time":200134,"text":"same building blocks with those same assumptions of trust."},{"time":204401,"text":"And that means that it's vulnerable"},{"time":207123,"text":"to certain kinds of mistakes that can happen,"},{"time":209519,"text":"or certain kinds of deliberate attacks,"},{"time":211380,"text":"but even the mistakes can be bad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":214485,"text":"So, for instance,"},{"time":217434,"text":"in all of Asia recently,"},{"time":219387,"text":"it was impossible to get YouTube for a little while"},{"time":222820,"text":"because Pakistan made some mistakes"},{"time":225100,"text":"in how it was censoring YouTube in its internal network."},{"time":228835,"text":"They didn't intend to screw up Asia, but they did"},{"time":231929,"text":"because of the way that the protocols work."},{"time":234833,"text":"Another example that may have affected many of you in this audience is,"},{"time":238057,"text":"you may remember a couple of years ago,"},{"time":240648,"text":"all the planes west of the Mississippi were grounded"},{"time":243461,"text":"because a single routing card in Salt Lake City"},{"time":246353,"text":"had a bug in it."},{"time":248715,"text":"Now, you don't really think"},{"time":250988,"text":"that our airplane system depends on the Internet,"},{"time":254014,"text":"and in some sense it doesn't."},{"time":255020,"text":"I'll come back to that later."},{"time":256636,"text":"But the fact is that people couldn't take off"},{"time":258886,"text":"because something was going wrong on the Internet,"},{"time":261161,"text":"and the router card was down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263736,"text":"And so, there are many of those things that start to happen."},{"time":267515,"text":"Now, there was an interesting thing that happened last April."},{"time":270654,"text":"All of a sudden,"},{"time":272180,"text":"a very large percentage of the traffic on the whole Internet,"},{"time":275512,"text":"including a lot of the traffic between U.S. military installations,"},{"time":279643,"text":"started getting re-routed through China."},{"time":282411,"text":"So for a few hours, it all passed through China."},{"time":285133,"text":"Now, China Telecom says it was just an honest mistake,"},{"time":289707,"text":"and it is actually possible that it was, the way things work,"},{"time":293564,"text":"but certainly somebody could make"},{"time":295599,"text":"a dishonest mistake of that sort if they wanted to,"},{"time":298872,"text":"and it shows you how vulnerable the system is even to mistakes."},{"time":302230,"text":"Imagine how vulnerable the system is to deliberate attacks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307151,"text":"So if somebody really wanted to attack the United States"},{"time":310549,"text":"or Western civilization these days,"},{"time":312641,"text":"they're not going to do it with tanks."},{"time":314830,"text":"That will not succeed."},{"time":317243,"text":"What they'll probably do is something"},{"time":319246,"text":"very much like the attack that happened"},{"time":322537,"text":"on the Iranian nuclear facility."},{"time":325244,"text":"Nobody has claimed credit for that."},{"time":327518,"text":"There was basically a factory of industrial machines."},{"time":331025,"text":"It didn't think of itself as being on the Internet."},{"time":333602,"text":"It thought of itself as being disconnected from the Internet,"},{"time":336189,"text":"but it was possible for somebody to smuggle"},{"time":338136,"text":"a USB drive in there, or something like that,"},{"time":340668,"text":"and software got in there that causes the centrifuges,"},{"time":344064,"text":"in that case, to actually destroy themselves."},{"time":347057,"text":"Now that same kind of software could destroy an oil refinery"},{"time":349723,"text":"or a pharmaceutical factory or a semiconductor plant."},{"time":354145,"text":"And so there's a lot of -- I'm sure you've read a lot in papers,"},{"time":357411,"text":"about worries about cyberattacks"},{"time":359602,"text":"and defenses against those."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362212,"text":"But the fact is, people are mostly focused on"},{"time":364192,"text":"defending the computers on the Internet,"},{"time":366475,"text":"and there's been surprisingly little attention"},{"time":368861,"text":"to defending the Internet itself as a communications medium."},{"time":373226,"text":"And I think we probably do need to pay"},{"time":375089,"text":"some more attention to that, because it's actually kind of fragile."},{"time":378177,"text":"So actually, in the early days,"},{"time":381104,"text":"back when it was the ARPANET,"},{"time":382828,"text":"there were actually times -- there was a particular time it failed completely"},{"time":386417,"text":"because one single message processor"},{"time":389702,"text":"actually got a bug in it."},{"time":392178,"text":"And the way the Internet works is"},{"time":394450,"text":"the routers are basically exchanging information"},{"time":398017,"text":"about how they can get messages to places,"},{"time":400607,"text":"and this one processor, because of a broken card,"},{"time":404505,"text":"decided it could actually get a message"},{"time":406514,"text":"to some place in negative time."},{"time":409202,"text":"So, in other words, it claimed it could deliver a message before you sent it."},{"time":413185,"text":"So of course, the fastest way to get a message anywhere"},{"time":416335,"text":"was to send it to this guy,"},{"time":418211,"text":"who would send it back in time and get it there super early,"},{"time":421758,"text":"so every message in the Internet"},{"time":424614,"text":"started getting switched through this one node,"},{"time":427856,"text":"and of course that clogged everything up."},{"time":429372,"text":"Everything started breaking."},{"time":431527,"text":"The interesting thing was, though,"},{"time":433567,"text":"that the sysadmins were able to fix it,"},{"time":435407,"text":"but they had to basically turn every single thing on the Internet off."},{"time":440189,"text":"Now, of course you couldn't do that today."},{"time":441587,"text":"I mean, everything off, it's like"},{"time":443981,"text":"the service call you get from the cable company,"},{"time":446213,"text":"except for the whole world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":449974,"text":"Now, in fact, they couldn't do it for a lot of reasons today."},{"time":452033,"text":"One of the reasons is a lot of their telephones"},{"time":454655,"text":"use IP protocol and use things like Skype and so on"},{"time":457624,"text":"that go through the Internet right now,"},{"time":459693,"text":"and so in fact we're becoming dependent on it"},{"time":462975,"text":"for more and more different things,"},{"time":464767,"text":"like when you take off from LAX,"},{"time":467705,"text":"you're really not thinking you're using the Internet."},{"time":469586,"text":"When you pump gas, you really don't think you're using the Internet."},{"time":473702,"text":"What's happening increasingly, though, is these systems"},{"time":475827,"text":"are beginning to use the Internet."},{"time":477694,"text":"Most of them aren't based on the Internet yet,"},{"time":480744,"text":"but they're starting to use the Internet for service functions,"},{"time":483280,"text":"for administrative functions,"},{"time":485185,"text":"and so if you take something like the cell phone system,"},{"time":488248,"text":"which is still relatively independent of the Internet for the most part,"},{"time":492568,"text":"Internet pieces are beginning to sneak into it"},{"time":495527,"text":"in terms of some of the control and administrative functions,"},{"time":499331,"text":"and it's so tempting to use these same building blocks"},{"time":501661,"text":"because they work so well, they're cheap,"},{"time":503925,"text":"they're repeated, and so on."},{"time":505025,"text":"So all of our systems, more and more,"},{"time":507797,"text":"are starting to use the same technology"},{"time":509577,"text":"and starting to depend on this technology."},{"time":511644,"text":"And so even a modern rocket ship these days"},{"time":514069,"text":"actually uses Internet protocol to talk"},{"time":516795,"text":"from one end of the rocket ship to the other."},{"time":518611,"text":"That's crazy. It was never designed to do things like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":521797,"text":"So we've built this system"},{"time":524914,"text":"where we understand all the parts of it,"},{"time":528024,"text":"but we're using it in a very, very different way than we expected to use it,"},{"time":531722,"text":"and it's gotten a very, very different scale"},{"time":534161,"text":"than it was designed for."},{"time":536332,"text":"And in fact, nobody really exactly understands"},{"time":539008,"text":"all the things it's being used for right now."},{"time":541271,"text":"It's turning into one of these big emergent systems"},{"time":543774,"text":"like the financial system, where we've designed all the parts"},{"time":547255,"text":"but nobody really exactly understands"},{"time":549861,"text":"how it operates and all the little details of it"},{"time":553088,"text":"and what kinds of emergent behaviors it can have."},{"time":555807,"text":"And so if you hear an expert talking about the Internet"},{"time":558940,"text":"and saying it can do this, or it does do this, or it will do that,"},{"time":561635,"text":"you should treat it with the same skepticism"},{"time":564096,"text":"that you might treat the comments of an economist about the economy"},{"time":568511,"text":"or a weatherman about the weather, or something like that."},{"time":570778,"text":"They have an informed opinion,"},{"time":573426,"text":"but it's changing so quickly that even the experts"},{"time":575967,"text":"don't know exactly what's going on."},{"time":577785,"text":"So if you see one of these maps of the Internet,"},{"time":580477,"text":"it's just somebody's guess."},{"time":582143,"text":"Nobody really knows what the Internet is right now"},{"time":584341,"text":"because it's different than it was an hour ago."},{"time":587082,"text":"It's constantly changing. It's constantly reconfiguring."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589883,"text":"And the problem with it is,"},{"time":591397,"text":"I think we are setting ourselves up for a kind of disaster"},{"time":594738,"text":"like the disaster we had in the financial system,"},{"time":597533,"text":"where we take a system that's basically built on trust,"},{"time":602877,"text":"was basically built for a smaller-scale system,"},{"time":605498,"text":"and we've kind of expanded it way beyond the limits"},{"time":608407,"text":"of how it was meant to operate."},{"time":610403,"text":"And so right now, I think it's literally true"},{"time":613671,"text":"that we don't know what the consequences"},{"time":617176,"text":"of an effective denial-of-service attack"},{"time":619610,"text":"on the Internet would be,"},{"time":621383,"text":"and whatever it would be is going to be worse next year,"},{"time":623257,"text":"and worse next year, and so on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":624665,"text":"But so what we need is a plan B."},{"time":627214,"text":"There is no plan B right now."},{"time":628846,"text":"There's no clear backup system that we've very carefully kept"},{"time":632349,"text":"to be independent of the Internet,"},{"time":634295,"text":"made out of completely different sets of building blocks."},{"time":637361,"text":"So what we need is something that doesn't necessarily"},{"time":640374,"text":"have to have the performance of the Internet,"},{"time":643108,"text":"but the police department has to be able"},{"time":644625,"text":"to call up the fire department even without the Internet,"},{"time":647148,"text":"or the hospitals have to order fuel oil."},{"time":649713,"text":"This doesn't need to be a multi-billion-dollar government project."},{"time":654327,"text":"It's actually relatively simple to do, technically,"},{"time":657075,"text":"because it can use existing fibers that are in the ground,"},{"time":660877,"text":"existing wireless infrastructure."},{"time":662836,"text":"It's basically a matter of deciding to do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":665601,"text":"But people won't decide to do it"},{"time":668085,"text":"until they recognize the need for it,"},{"time":670464,"text":"and that's the problem that we have right now."},{"time":671962,"text":"So there's been plenty of people,"},{"time":674745,"text":"plenty of us have been quietly arguing"},{"time":677789,"text":"that we should have this independent system for years,"},{"time":680707,"text":"but it's very hard to get people focused on plan B"},{"time":683716,"text":"when plan A seems to be working so well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":687390,"text":"So I think that, if people understand"},{"time":690819,"text":"how much we're starting to depend on the Internet,"},{"time":693873,"text":"and how vulnerable it is,"},{"time":695850,"text":"we could get focused on"},{"time":697956,"text":"just wanting this other system to exist,"},{"time":700980,"text":"and I think if enough people say, \"Yeah, I would like to use it,"},{"time":704057,"text":"I'd like to have such a system,\" then it will get built."},{"time":707067,"text":"It's not that hard a problem."},{"time":708490,"text":"It could definitely be done by people in this room."}]},{"cues":[{"time":711725,"text":"And so I think that this is actually,"},{"time":716084,"text":"of all the problems you're going to hear about at the conference,"},{"time":719263,"text":"this is probably one of the very easiest to fix."},{"time":721941,"text":"So I'm happy to get a chance to tell you about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":724708,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":727319,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}